      "FullName": "Sandbox.RealTimeSince",
      "Name": "RealTimeSince",
      "Documentation": {
        "Summary": "A convenience struct to easily measure time since an event last happened, based on <see cref=\"P:Sandbox.RealTime.GlobalNow\" />.<br /><br />\nTypical usage would see you assigning 0 to a variable of this type to reset the timer.\nThen the struct would return time since the last reset. i.e.:\n<code>\nRealTimeSince lastUsed = 0;\nif ( lastUsed &gt; 10 ) { /*Do something*/ }\n</code>"
      },
      "DocId": "T:Sandbox.RealTimeSince"
    },
